    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though the car lacks the smooth performance of a newer model. You will notice some visible wear on the interior upholstery and a few minor scratches and dings on the exterior. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, making it a solid choice for practical transportation at an affordable price point.",
